{
  "stem": "13096.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in many-- in many speeches that he made, he say, anti-Semitism, it doesn't exist in Italy, and because we are all Italians, and we are-- but after, you know, this, he start having, you know, friendship with Hitler and all this, everything start to change.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the first thing they-- they start making, you know, these martial laws.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was terrible because we didn't expect it, and we didn't even dream to have those treatments.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When, you know, Hitler and Mussolini become aligned, you see?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the first thing it was, like, in 1938.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 1938, we were just out of the blue, as I say, not many of them-- of course, we had a radio to listen to.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we opened the newspaper, but we-- we used to have the newspaper every day, and the-- the-- the first thing we saw into the newspaper, there were like the face of a Jew with distorted nose, distorted eyes.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the people, they were trying now to show that the Jews, they were ugly and like, like Satans or whatever.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they start-- you know, and-- and we read all the laws about-- about the Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First off, you know, there were many laws, like you say.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For instance-- the-- the first thing, for instance, all the people, all the soldiers, all the soldiers in the army, even the captains were-- and people that were-- that were, you know, served their country in Italy-- not in Rhodes Island, we are not so many, in Italy.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were sent away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were not allowed to serve in the Army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, you know, the Jews, they were not allowed to close their shops on Saturday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They-- they were not allowed to observe the festival.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
